unnecessary memory wastage
to overcame this we use StringBuilder.

-----
StringBuilder :- 
it is a Class
present in the "Lang" package
import java.lang.StringBuilder;
it is used to create mutable string objects.
object of StringBuilder can be modified after it is created.
StringBuilder class provides methods to manipulate the string such as append, insert, delete, reverse, etc.
StringBuilder is more efficient than String when it comes to concatenation and modification of strings.